"Contribution" means any original work of authorship, including any
modification or addition to an existing work, that is intentionally submitted
by You to the Project for inclusion in the Project.

"Submit" means any form of electronic, verbal, or written communication sent
to the Project or its representatives, including but not limited to code,
documentation, issues, and pull requests.

